      "pattern": "This conversation shows a classic breadcrumbing pattern where one person says they can't move on while simultaneously saying dismissive phrases like 'good luck or whatever.' The mix of declarations of love followed by emotional distance creates confusion — warm words paired with cold energy. This push-pull dynamic keeps you emotionally engaged while the other person maintains control of the connection without real commitment.",
