      "exercise": "Try this grounding exercise: Place both feet flat on the floor. Take a slow breath in for 4 counts, hold for 4, exhale for 6. As you breathe, say internally: 'I release what isn't mine to carry.' Do this 5 times. Then write down one concrete thing you know to be true about yourself that has nothing to do with this relationship — remind yourself of the solid ground beneath you that no one else can shake.",
